These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, time-travel, comedy
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the owner of the goldfish##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | time-travel | family |
| Pet           | goldfish  | rabbit     | guinea-pig  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, metal, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, train, ship
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the person driving the train##7
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | funk | hip-hop |
| Transport     | train       | ship     | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, soy-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, ship
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person driving the quad-bike##7
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | fanta | cola | soy-milk  |
| Transport   | ship  | jet-ski  | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, mechanic, writer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, sports, martial-arts
1. the doctor is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the mechanic##7
2. the person watching sports movies is not the doctor##6
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | mechanic | doctor | writer     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | satire          | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, gospel, funk
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, subway
1. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the fan of gospel##7
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | funk     | gospel   |
| Transport     | subway | train | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, gospel, ambient
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, canadian, nigerian
1. the indian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
2. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the nigerian and the fan of pop##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | gospel     | pop     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | canadian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person who's sport is climbing##7
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | guinea-pig       | dog      | turtle       |
| Sport   | climbing | handball | rowing |

