The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, family, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the engineer##7
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | photographer | dancer  | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy      | crime | family      |

