.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, accountant, librarian
1. the librarian is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
2. the accountant is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the bartender is somewhere between the accountant and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | sudoku | video-games   |
| Job     | librarian    | bartender  | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, volleyball
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's sport is climbing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | juice    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | volleyball | rowing | climbing |

