.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, cherry, orange
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, spy, musical
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person eating potato##7
3. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | orange       | cherry     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | thriller | spy |

