2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of blues and the person drinking 7up##7
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | water | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | blues | indie    | reggae |

