.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, fanta
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, doctor, paramedic
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the musician##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the doctor##7
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | sprite      | fanta     | lemonade |
| Job        | paramedic | musician | doctor    |

 